==French==
===Noun===
# [[wheel]]
#: ''Une roue de vélo'' (bike wheel), ''une roue de secours'' (spare wheel)
#: ''Roue de moulin'' : mill wheel.
#: ''Roue dentée'' (or ''engrenage'') : toothed wheel.
# An old torture, the penalty of the wheel : ''le supplice de la roue''. See [[rouer]].

